{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"15":{"eng-name":"Jihad (Kitab Al-Jihad)","ara-name":"كتاب الجهاد"}},"section_detail":{"15":{"hadithnumber_first":2477,"hadithnumber_last":2787,"arabicnumber_first":2477,"arabicnumber_last":2787}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":2593,"arabicnumber":2593,"text":"حَدَّثَنَا عُقْبَةُ بْنُ مُكْرَمٍ، حَدَّثَنَا سَلْمُ بْنُ قُتَيْبَةَ الشَّعِيرِيُّ، عَنْ شُعْبَةَ، عَنْ سِمَاكٍ، عَنْ رَجُلٍ، مِنْ قَوْمِهِ عَنْ آخَرَ، مِنْهُمْ قَالَ رَأَيْتُ رَايَةَ رَسُولِ اللَّهِ صلى الله عليه وسلم صَفْرَاءَ ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":15,"hadith":117},"chapter":{"id":76,"ara-name":"باب فِي الرَّايَاتِ وَالأَلْوِيَةِ","eng-name":"On Flags And Banners","isFirstHadith":false}}]}